Package com.octo.captcha.component.image.color

Color component package
In this package you will find color generator

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ColorGenerator ColorGenerator is an interface used by TextPaster to generate color for rendering each character with specific color.
 

Class Summary
RandomListColorGenerator A RandomListColor returns a random color have been picked from a user defined colors list.
RandomRangeColorGenerator A RandomRangeColorGenerator returns a random color whose components (red, green, blue and alpha) have been picked from user defined ranges.
SingleColorGenerator Simple color generator that always return the same color
